preference.name: GMO_enable_new_pnum_match_criteria
preference.preference_description: Enables the additional check for EWO_status to Usage attributes when a Usage is given a red Part Number match, for a new Part Number match it is set from fail to partial pass. This preference is added as part of GRDVA Phase 3 project. By default, this is activated. This is a Site preference.
